00:20:26,630 --> 00:20:29,730
and broke it into half.

249
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:32,240
It looks like Cao Xihe

250
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:35,500
is competing in strength against Sheng Jingchu today.

251
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:48,530
Regardless of the momentum or the moves,

252
00:20:48,530 --> 00:20:52,230
Cao Xihe has gradually taken the advantage.

253
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:26,800
How does the game look now?

254
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:29,430
Can Sheng Jingchu win?

255
00:21:29,430 --> 00:21:31,310
It's hard to say.

256
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:35,870
Both Senior Brother Jing and Senior Brother He are players with strong killing auras.

257
00:21:35,870 --> 00:21:38,520
They really aren't giving in to each other today.

258
00:21:39,430 --> 00:21:42,140
Cao Xihe is so aggressive in his attacks today.

259
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:44,560
If he wins, he'll have to fight against Master in the final match. If he knew that,

260
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:46,730
he'd be scared to death.

261
00:22:04,430 --> 00:22:06,640
Senior Brother Jing.

262
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:09,530
- I need to go to the bathroom.
- Go ahead.

263
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,420
Why did he run away?

264
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:16,350
He's going to the restroom. Nature calls.

265
00:22:16,350 --> 00:22:18,970
But whose time is counted when he goes to the restroom?

266
00:22:18,970 --> 00:22:21,160
It's not to the countdown time yet, so the GO clock doesn't stop,

267
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:23,610
of course, it's counting down his own time.

268
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:29,340
Xie Hanzhou has already entered the final match.

269
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:31,720
Just waiting to see if Sheng Jingchu will defeat Cao Xihe.

270
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:35,120
I'd actually like to see Cao Xihe go up against Master Xie.

271
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:06,750
Cao Xihe, 8th dan, was sailing smoothly before the 80th move.

272
00:23:06,750 --> 00:23:11,570
The 9th dan, Sheng Jingchu's black stone on the bottom right is in jeopardy.

273
00:23:11,570 --> 00:23:14,210
But when Cao Xihe returned from the bathroom,

274
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:16,270
there seems to be hesitation in his moves now.

275
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:18,670
Not sure what he's pondering about?

276
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:05,020
Sheng Jingchu's game structure is very sharp.

277
00:24:05,020 --> 00:24:08,580
When he was surrounded around by the white stones, he managed to find a crack.

278
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:11,510
Cao Xihe seems to have missed Sheng Jingchu's smart move.

279
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:15,240
Will these two moves be this game's turning point?

280
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:43,680
Cao Xihe stopped the clock and declared defeat. Sheng Jingchu wins!

281
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,860
What's going on?

282
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:50,160
He had a leading advantage and yet he chickened out now?

283
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:52,290
What is he doing?

284
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:56,660
What's going on with Cao Xihe? Is he scaring himself?

285
00:24:56,660 --> 00:24:58,910
What happened?

286
00:25:05,690 --> 00:25:07,280
You...

287
00:25:32,820 --> 00:25:35,550
Big Brother, stop looking at me like that.

288
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:38,790
I know I'm good-looking, but I can't resist your stare.

289
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:45,400
Why did you lose so quickly all of a sudden?

290
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:49,110
Big Brother, now you're bullying me. I lost so I'm already in a bad mood.

291
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:51,920
And now you're here rubbing more salt into the wound.

292
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:56,400
Do I need a reason to lose? Let say my skill is not up to par.

293
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,630
But this isn't your true skill level.

294
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:12,530
Is the truth really that important? Big Brother?

295
00:26:12,530 --> 00:26:14,370
I know I'll lose to you eventually.

296
00:26:14,370 --> 00:26:16,570
If I lose sooner, we can have dinner sooner.

297
00:26:16,570 --> 00:26:18,690
You're not feeling well, so you can turn in earlier. Right?

298
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:20,110
Best of both worlds!

299
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:22,460
Let's go, get some rest.

300
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:35,130
You do not want to play against Master in the finals, is that it?

301
00:26:43,570 --> 00:26:47,510
Do you remember what Master taught us in our very first lesson?

302
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:51,710
When you make your move, you have to respect your opponent.

303
00:26:51,710 --> 00:26:54,940
If you want to lose, you can.

304
00:26:55,890 --> 00:26:58,690
I'll also try my very best to win the game.

305
00:26:58,690 --> 00:27:01,060
But what exactly were you doing?

306
00:27:20,230 --> 00:27:24,780
I'm sorry, I was just passing by... You two, please carry on.

307
00:27:29,740 --> 00:27:31,250
Don't move!

308
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:35,650
- I'm... I'm... I'm fine, it's nothing.

309
00:27:35,650 --> 00:27:38,660
- Does it hurt?
- I-I'm fine.

310
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:40,230
Go to the hospital in a bit and get this checked.

311
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:43,610
It's such a small scratch. I bump into things all the time. Really, I'm fine.

312
00:27:43,610 --> 00:27:45,620
How come your hands are so warm?

313
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:48,420
- Do you have a fever?
- I'm fine.

314
00:27:50,380 --> 00:27:54,380
Are you sure? Let's go! I'm fine.

315
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:03,440
Hurry up! Pour me some.

316
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:06,520
Go easy on the drinks.

317
00:28:06,520 --> 00:28:10,340
You need to enjoy this 8-year-old liquor in small sips.

318
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:14,510
"Drinking is most pleasant when not being urged. Playing chess without struggling is the true form of winning."

319
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:19,090
Go with the flow. There will be losses and wins. That's how you'll always be happy. Pour it.

320
00:28:19,090 --> 00:28:20,960
I'm not encouraging you to drink more.

321
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:23,420
But it's even worse to urge me to drink less.

322
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:25,620
Pour me some!

323
00:28:34,390 --> 00:28:36,250
Here you go!

324
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:47,190
Sheng Jingchu beat Cao Xihe in the semi-finals. You beat Uncle Jiang.

325
00:28:47,190 --> 00:28:49,950
You will be facing Jingchu in the finals.

326
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:56,550
Well, they are all my disciples, I treat them all the same.

327
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:58,160
The same?

328
00:28:58,780 --> 00:29:02,220
You brat, why are you looking at me like that?

329
00:29:07,250 --> 00:29:10,140
Jingchu won Tianyuan at 16.
 (T/N: A famous GO competition in China.)

330
00:29:10,150 --> 00:29:13,170
Next year, I beat him once in a competition.

331
00:29:13,180 --> 00:29:15,750
Since he left Jiuzhou Hall at 18,

332
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:19,280
I have not formally played against him in a competition.

333
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:23,460
It's really hard to predict with his current ability.

334
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:26,690
I'm really looking forward to playing a few games with him.

335
00:29:26,690 --> 00:29:29,700
Do you think you can beat him?

336
00:29:29,700 --> 00:29:32,070
It's hard to say.

337
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:36,440
If he beats me, that would be wonderful!

338
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:40,770
If you lose, it wouldn't be pretty.

339
00:29:40,770 --> 00:29:45,020
Hey. Is that really what you think of your dad?

340
00:29:45,020 --> 00:29:48,380
GO was the minority in the eye of Confucius,

341
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:52,170
but now it is one of the four traditional forms of art.

342
00:29:52,170 --> 00:29:53,580
What did it rely on to get there?

343
00:29:53,580 --> 00:29:56,730
Isn't it all based on the masters passing it onto their disciples?

344
00:29:58,170 --> 00:30:01,620
Do you know what the masters really want to see?

345
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:04,580
To see their students surpass them.

346
00:30:04,580 --> 00:30:06,820
If all the disciples can't beat their masters,

347
00:30:06,820 --> 00:30:09,330
then what GO skills are there to pass on?

348
00:30:09,330 --> 00:30:10,860
It's not that, Dad.

349
00:30:10,860 --> 00:30:14,980
You've won so many competitions, but the one you never won was the Legends of China Competition.

350
00:30:14,980 --> 00:30:16,830
You finally beat Uncle Jiang in the semi-finals,

351
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:20,510
if you lose to Jingchu this time, you'll have to wait 3 more years for another chance to win.

352
00:30:20,510 --> 00:30:22,250
What if...

353
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:29,520
I'm only saying what if you can't take the championship at the Legends of China Competition.

354
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:32,530
This wouldn't be something you'd regret in your life?

355
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:38,530
If I lose to Jingchu, I won't have any regrets.

356
00:30:38,530 --> 00:30:42,540
[7th GO Legends of China Competition - Welcome]

357
00:30:54,590 --> 00:30:56,450
Coming.

358
00:30:58,020 --> 00:31:01,400
Hello, Mr. Sheng Jingchu asked us to bring this over to you.

359
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:04,220
Thank you.

360
00:31:04,220 --> 00:31:07,480
This guy, he's already that sick

361
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:09,810
and he still thinks of me.

362
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:17,460
Fever, headache, soreness in arms and legs...

363
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:20,370
Coming.

364
00:31:30,330 --> 00:31:32,250
Why are you here?

365
00:31:32,250 --> 00:31:33,310
I am here to give you—

366
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,550
How's your leg? Is it better?

367
00:31:34,550 --> 00:31:37,930
I'm good. I'm good. Get up, get up.

368
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:43,820
You have a fever!

369
00:31:43,820 --> 00:31:47,050
Hurry, go get some rest. Hurry up!

370
00:31:54,830 --> 00:31:57,320
I'm going to bring you some warm water.

371
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:00,300
- Be careful of your leg.
- It's fine.

372
00:32:24,520 --> 00:32:27,250
- Thanks.
- You don't need to thank me.

373
00:32:27,250 --> 00:32:28,850
This is all part of what I should be doing.

374
00:32:28,850 --> 00:32:31,580
At the end of the day, I'm your assistant.

375
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:36,580
Also, you have a fever because you were waiting for me.

376
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:38,490
If this is going to affect your upcoming competition,

377
00:32:38,490 --> 00:32:41,550
I wouldn't be able to forgive myself.

378
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,760
Cheng Liao.

379
00:33:01,740 --> 00:33:04,100
Let me teach you how to play GO.

380
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:09,820
You have a fever, you should rest.

381
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:14,750
Don't you think it's too quiet this way?

382
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,140
The sequence to playing GO is

383
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:23,710
"Black First, White After"

384
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:27,950
I know, this spot here,

385
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:29,540
it's called "Xing Wei."

386
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:32,670
That's correct, it's called "Xing Wei."
 (T/N: The four corner points on the GO board.)

387
00:33:32,670 --> 00:33:34,840
And how about this one?

388
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:38,100
This one's called "Tian Yuan."
 (T/N: The center point on the GO board.)

389
00:33:40,840 --> 00:33:45,080
If Black wants to take a corner in the first move,

390
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:49,850
it needs to be placed in its own upper right corner.

391
00:33:49,850 --> 00:33:52,980
This move is called "Jing Shou."
 (T/N: Literally respectful move.)

392
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:55,460
It leaves the corner that's closest to the opponent

393
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:59,280
to them to show respect.

394
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:02,020
It's also the etiquette in playing GO.

395
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:05,670
Can Black play its first move

396
00:34:05,670 --> 00:34:09,700
at Tian Yuan?
 (T/N: The center point on the GO board.)

397
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,700
Of course, it can.

398
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:20,600
This is how your hand should hold a GO stone.

399
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:24,700
The middle finger is above, and the index finger is below.

400
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:26,380
Hold the stone.

401
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:29,180
The fingers bend a little.

402
00:34:29,180 --> 00:34:32,810
Looking at it from the side, it looks like an eagle's beak.

403
00:34:34,490 --> 00:34:36,170
Try it.

404
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:47,650
The strength while holding the stone

405
00:34:47,650 --> 00:34:49,260
can't be too light

406
00:34:49,260 --> 00:34:50,930
or too heavy.

407
00:34:50,930 --> 00:34:53,070
If it's too light, the stone may fall off.

408
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:55,670
If it's too strong, it can be squeezed out.

409
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:57,170
Watch.

410
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,520
Try it again.

411
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:09,310
Much better.

412
00:35:09,310 --> 00:35:12,230
Just think. When I learn how to play GO from you,

413
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:14,900
I have to start by learning how to hold the stone.

414
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:17,340
This is like a huge engineering project.

415
00:35:17,340 --> 00:35:18,940
You even have a fever now.

416
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:20,520
You should hurry and rest.

417
00:35:20,520 --> 00:35:24,480
Otherwise, I'll feel guilty again.

418
00:35:25,770 --> 00:35:27,300
The water is done boiling.

419
00:35:27,300 --> 00:35:29,000
Let me get another cup of hot water for you.

420
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,540
You should hurry and take the medicine.

421
00:35:30,540 --> 00:35:33,150
Rest more, drink more water.

422
00:35:33,150 --> 00:35:34,560
You got this!

423
00:36:01,210 --> 00:36:02,720
- Master.
- Jingchu.

424
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:04,300
I heard that you were sick.

425
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:06,480
Why didn't you tell me that you had a fever?

426
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:09,940
Hurry, hurry! Sit down.

427
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:12,700
Here, here. Lay here.

428
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:14,600
Why didn't you tell me?

429
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:17,540
I'm fine, Master. You don't need to worry about me.

430
00:36:17,540 --> 00:36:21,240
I've taken medicine, I'll be fine soon.

431
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:23,430
Took medicine?

432
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:26,120
Ever since you entered the hall at six years old,

433
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:29,560
I've never seen you take any medicine.

434
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:31,490
I took one pill.

435
00:36:32,130 --> 00:36:34,590
When you used to catch a cold, have a fever,

436
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:36,510
it was like I was trying to kill you trying to get you to take medicine.

437
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:38,380
No matter what you wouldn't take it.

438
00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:41,420
Why are you so obedient this time in taking the medicine?

439
00:36:42,220 --> 00:36:44,920
A friend... gave it to me.

440
00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:48,900
Cheng Liao?

441
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:50,810
How did you know?

442
00:36:51,610 --> 00:36:53,700
I haven't seen this girl yet.

443
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:56,420
When will you bring her and let me take a look?

444
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:58,930
I'll check her out for you.

445
00:36:59,490 --> 00:37:01,840
Master, we...

446
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:05,770
- I'll pour some water for you.
- Don't move. Don't move. Let me feel.

447
00:37:06,450 --> 00:37:08,300
How did your fever get so high?

448
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:11,370
Stay still, don't move. Wait a moment.

449
00:37:16,520 --> 00:37:19,990
Here, keep this on.

450
00:37:19,990 --> 00:37:21,590
Lie down. Lie down.

451
00:37:25,970 --> 00:37:27,860
Master.

452
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:31,070
When can I return to Jiuzhou Hall?

453
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:35,120
At that time, I told you to go out and become independent in life.

454
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:37,760
It was because I didn't want you to be

455
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:40,980
trapped in the limited space of the hall

456
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:42,460
at such a young age.

457
00:37:42,460 --> 00:37:45,850
Remember this. If a GO player doesn't know how to live

458
00:37:45,850 --> 00:37:48,300
and all he thinks about is playing GO,

459
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:52,270
then he won't be able to elevate to a higher level either.

460
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,760
Take it slowly. Don't rush.

461
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,550
At least, right now

462
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:58,450
isn't the time yet.

463
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:03,590
Hurry up and deliver these to the guests.

464
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:05,580
Okay.

465
00:38:08,090 --> 00:38:10,540
Miss Cheng, I discussed this with the head chef already.

466
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,890
He said he won't cook any dishes that he's not familiar with,

467
00:38:12,890 --> 00:38:16,820
