468
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:18,890
I can use the kitchen?

469
00:38:18,890 --> 00:38:22,860
We're willing to satisfy the competition players' requests as much as possible.

470
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:25,650
But you must move fast. We can only give you 40 minutes.

471
00:38:25,650 --> 00:38:26,940
Okay. That's no problem. No problem.

472
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:29,730
Do you need anything? You can tell the head chef.

473
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:33,510
I think this should be enough.

474
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:36,130
- Thank you. I've bothered you.
- That's fine. No problem.

